Interface Summary
IAggregator Interface for the AMD Aggregator.
IAggregator.SubstitutionTransformer Transformer interface used by IAggregator.substituteProps(String, SubstitutionTransformer).
IAggregatorExtension Interface for a registered aggregator extension.
IExtensionInitializer Initialization interface for aggregator extensions.
IExtensionInitializer.IExtensionRegistrar Interface that can be used by Aggregator extensions to register additional IResourceFactory or IModuleBuilder extensions.
IRequestListener Listener interface for HTTP request processing.
IShutdownListener Listener interface for shutdown notification.
IVariableResolver  
 

Class Summary
InitParams Wrapper class for aggregator init-params.
InitParams.InitParam Init params are name/value pairs
 

Exception Summary
BadRequestException Extends ServletException for incorrect or improperly formated requests.
DependencyVerificationException An exception that's thrown by the JavaScript optimizer when it detects that the dependency list of a module has changed from what was used to generate the dependency graph and development mode is enabled
NotFoundException Extends ServletException for resource not found errors.
ProcessingDependenciesException Thrown when the aggregator is servicing a request the dependency graph is in the process of being built/validated, and development mode is enabled.
